  "QuestText": {
    "QuestInfo": [
      {
        "Language": "JPN",
        "Name": "\u738B\u8005\u3001\u6EB6\u5CA9\u6D1E\u306B\u964D\u308A\u7ACB\u3064",
        "Client": "\u5C3B\u5C3E\u306E\u7126\u3052\u305F\u30A2\u30A4\u30EB\u30FC",
        "Description": "\u3072\u3001\u3072\u3069\u3044\u76EE\u306B\u3042\u3063\u305F\u306E\u30CB\u30E3\uFF5E\uFF01\r\n\u6EB6\u5CA9\u6D1E\u306B\u304A\u3063\u304B\u306A\u3044\u30EA\u30AA\u30EC\u30A6\u30B9\u304C\r\n\u73FE\u308C\u305F\u306E\u30CB\u30E3\uFF01\u3000\u3042\u3044\u3064\u306E\u708E\u3092\r\n\u6D74\u3073\u305F\u305B\u3044\u3067\u3001\u30DC\u30AF\u306E\u81EA\u6162\u306E\u5C3B\u5C3E\r\n\u304C\u7126\u3052\u3061\u3083\u3063\u305F\u306E\u30CB\u30E3\u30A1\u2026\u3002\r\n\u30CF\u30F3\u30BF\u30FC\u3055\u3093\u3082\u72E9\u731F\u3059\u308B\u6642\u306F\r\n\u5927\u4E8B\u306A\u5C3B\u5C3E\u306B\u6C17\u3092\u4ED8\u3051\u308B\u30CB\u30E3\u2026\u3002",
        "Target": "\u30EA\u30AA\u30EC\u30A6\u30B9\uFF11\u982D\u306E\u72E9\u731F",
        "Fail": "\u5831\u916C\u91D1\u30BC\u30ED\r\n\u30BF\u30A4\u30E0\u30A2\u30C3\u30D7"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Champion of the Caverns",
        "Client": "Felyne with a Singed Tail",
        "Description": "Meow, I\u0027ve seen my share of Raths\r\nbefore. Never thought they were that\r\ntough, just fly around and yowl at ya.\r\nMewboy, I was so wrong... I got the\r\nbig idea to take one on, paw-to-claw,\r\nand it only took one fireball for me\r\nto hightail it out of there! Youch!",
        "Target": "Hunt a Rathalos",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Champion des Cavernes",
        "Client": "Felyne \u00E0 queue br\u00FBl\u00E9e",
        "Description": "Miaou, j\u0027en ai vu passer des\r\nRathalos, mais je les pensais plus\r\neffrayants que dangereux. J\u0027avais\r\ntort... Je me suis dit que j\u0027allais\r\nen affronter un avec mes petites\r\npapattes... et une boule de feu a\r\nsuffit pour me faire d\u00E9taler !",
        "Target": "Chasser un Rathalos",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Il campione delle caverne",
        "Client": "Felyne dalla coda bruciata",
        "Description": "Miao, ho visto dei Rathalos\r\nprima d\u0027ora, ma mai avrei\r\npensato che fossero cos\u00EC\r\nostici. Per me volavano e\r\nululavano. Mi sbagliavo... Ho\r\npensato di sfidarne uno, ma\r\nuna palla di fuoco \u00E8 bastata!",
        "Target": "Caccia un Rathalos",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Meister der H\u00F6hlen",
        "Client": "Leicht angesengter Felyne",
        "Description": "Miau, ich hab schon einige Raths\r\ngesehen. Hab sie nie f\u00FCr so z\u00E4h ge-\r\nhalten; dachte, sie fliegen rum und\r\njaulen. Katzblitz, lag ich falsch... Ich\r\nhatte die super Idee, gegen einen zu\r\nk\u00E4mpfen. Ein Feuerball reichte, dann\r\nbin ich abgehauen! Uff!",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Rathalos.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Campe\u00F3n de las cavernas",
        "Client": "Felyne de cola chamuscada",
        "Description": "Ya hab\u00EDa visto antes a los\r\nRathalos, pero no pens\u00E9 que\r\nfuesen tan fuertes. Se me\r\nocurri\u00F3 luchar contra uno,\r\npero le bast\u00F3 una bola de\r\nfuego para hacerme salir\r\npitando de all\u00ED.",
        "Target": "Caza un Rathalos",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u0412\u043E\u0438\u0442\u0435\u043B\u044C \u0438\u0437 \u043F\u0435\u0449\u0435\u0440",
        "Client": "\u041A\u043E\u0442\u0442 \u0441 \u043E\u043F\u0430\u043B\u0435\u043D\u043D\u044B\u043C \u0445\u0432\u043E\u0441\u0442\u043E\u043C",
        "Description": "\u042F, \u043A\u043E\u043D\u0435\u0447\u043D\u043E, \u0443\u0436\u0435 \u0432\u0438\u0434\u0435\u043B \u0440\u0430\u0437\u043D\u044B\u0445\r\n\u0420\u0430\u0442\u0430\u043B\u043E\u0441\u043E\u0432. \u0412\u043E\u0442 \u0442\u043E\u043B\u044C\u043A\u043E \u043D\u0435 \u0434\u0443\u043C\u0430\u043B\r\n\u044F, \u0447\u0442\u043E \u043E\u043D\u0438 \u0442\u0430\u043A\u0438\u0435 \u0441\u0438\u043B\u044C\u043D\u044B\u0435...\r\n\u0417\u0430\u0445\u043E\u0442\u0435\u043B \u0441\u0446\u0435\u043F\u0438\u0442\u044C\u0441\u044F \u0441 \u0442\u0430\u043A\u0438\u043C \u043E\u0434\u0438\u043D\r\n\u043D\u0430 \u043E\u0434\u0438\u043D, \u0430 \u043F\u043E\u0442\u043E\u043C \u0431\u0435\u0436\u0430\u043B, \u0447\u0442\u043E\r\n\u0435\u0441\u0442\u044C \u0441\u0438\u043B, \u043E\u0442 \u043E\u0434\u043D\u043E\u0433\u043E \u043E\u0433\u043D\u0435\u043D\u043D\u043E\u0433\u043E\r\n\u0448\u0430\u0440\u0430! \u041E\u0445!",
        "Target": "\u0412\u044B\u0441\u043B\u0435\u0434\u0438\u0442\u044C \u0420\u0430\u0442\u0430\u043B\u043E\u0441\u0430",
        "Fail": "\u0421\u0447\u0435\u0442\u0447\u0438\u043A \u043D\u0430\u0433\u0440\u0430\u0434\u044B \u0434\u043E\u0445\u043E\u0434\u0438\u0442 \u0434\u043E 0\r\n\u0438\u043B\u0438 \u0438\u0441\u0442\u0435\u043A\u0430\u0435\u0442 \u0432\u0440\u0435\u043C\u044F"
      },
      {
        "Language": "POL",
        "Name": "Mistrz z Jaskini",
        "Client": "Felin z przypalonym ogonem",
        "Description": "Miau, widzia\u0142em ju\u017C w \u017Cyciu sporo\r\nRath\u00F3w. Nie uwa\u017Ca\u0142em ich za gro\u017Ane\r\n\u2013 lata to co\u015B tylko w k\u00F3\u0142ko i wyje.\r\nNo i si\u0119 zdziwi\u0142em! Raz zachcia\u0142o\r\nmi si\u0119 takiego zaczepi\u0107 i jak pu\u015Bci\u0142\r\nkul\u0119 ognia, to od razu zmyka\u0142em\r\nz podwini\u0119tym ogonem! Miau\u0107!",
        "Target": "Upoluj Rathalosa",
        "Fail": "Nagroda = 0 lub koniec czasu"
      },
      {
        "Language": "POR",
        "Name": "Campe\u00E3o das cavernas",
        "Client": "Felyno com cauda queimada",
        "Description": "Miau, eu j\u00E1 vi minha cota de Raths na\r\nvida. Nunca pensei que elas fossem t\u00E3o\r\nduronas, voando por a\u00ED e uivando pra\r\ngente. Cara, eu como eu tava errado...\r\nTive a genial ideia de enfrentar uma,\r\ngarra a garra, e bastou uma bola de\r\nfogo pra eu fugir de l\u00E1! Iau!",
        "Target": "Cace um Rathalos",
        "Fail": "A recompensa chega a 0\r\nou o tempo expira"
      },
